===Etymology 1===
{{ja-kanjitab|みの|yomi=k|alt=簑}}
{{swp|ja:蓑}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|蓑|tr=mi₁no₂}}, ultimately from {{inh|ja|jpx-pro|*minə}}. The word is presumably attested in Old Japanese phonetically in Shōsōin documents<!--古文書一、大宝二年 Taihō year 2, so 702-->, where "{{lang|ja|母宇治部'''弥乃'''売}}" is lined up with "{{lang|ja|妻物部小'''蓑'''売}}".<ref name="JDB">{{R:Jidai-betsu Kokugo Daijiten|page=714}}</ref>

